dct_title_s: Map of The Cohansey River, in the City of Bridgeton, Cumberland County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map shows the exterior lines for solid filling, established by the Riparian Commissioners. Map also shows Dredging line for channel proposed in 1872, and a few of the streets on either side of the river. There are 6 of this same map bound together
